items.title: Trump says deal to end Gaza war is 'very close'
items.description: U.S. President Donald Trump said on Wednesday that a deal to end the war in Gaza was "very close" and that he might travel to Egypt this weekend."

items.title: Trump says he may go to Egypt soon for Gaza deal
items.description: President Donald Trump said on Wednesday he may travel to Egypt this weekend as his negotiators seek to seal a Gaza hostages-for-ceasefire deal.
